sentence: A look at the weighted underlying holdings of the Consumer Discretionary Select Sector SPDR Fund ( XLY ) shows an impressive 11.1% of holdings on a weighted basis have experienced insider buying within the past six months.

Home Depot Inc (Symbol: HD), which makes up 7.09% of the Consumer Discretionary Select Sector SPDR Fund ( XLY ), has seen 2 directors and officers purchase shares in the past six months, according to the recent Form 4 data.
The ETF holds a total of $768,583,098 worth of HD, making it the #3 largest holding.
